column5: guys im in barrie..i forgot to renew my license yesterday and everything is closed including my local bait shop..any ideas where i can get this done on a closed down day
If you're going ice fishing some of the hut operators may sell stickers or you can renew online at the MNR site  jjcanoe
I think you can do it on line and print a temporary license  https://outdoorscard.mnr.gov.on.ca/english/...?tid=0&s=20

hey guys got the problem solved...love 2 fish in lefroy is open until 5 today...you can get everything yo need there  4line of innisfil through lefroy pass the shell follow road to left it turns into belle ewart....it will be on your left  phone number 705 456 8745  thanks for the feedback guys..hope i helped someone out as well
Yeah thats the link but I couldn't find it!  jjcanoe
